ERROR #1 : PERTAMA KALI RUN SETELAH INSTALL NODEJS

Install NodeJS di
🔗 https://nodejs.org/

⚠️Saat mau RUN malah Error⚠️
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

PS C:\Users\Indri\Desktop\COBA-NODE> node code.js
node : The term 'node' is not recognized as the name of a cmdlet, function, script file, or operable program. Check the spelling of the name, or if a path was 
included, verify that the path is correct and try again.
At line:1 char:1
+ node code.js
+ ~~~~
    + CategoryInfo          : ObjectNotFound: (node:String) [], CommandNotFoundException
    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : CommandNotFoundException

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Coba cek apakah instalasi sudah terpasang
   buka gitbash >> (ketik) node-v >> muncul version node js (Jika instalasi awal berhasil)
2. Cek Path NodeJS
   (Ini cara Windows)
   Folder >> This PC >> (Klik Kanan) >> Properties >> Advanced system Settings >> (Paling Bawah) Environment Variables >> (System Variabel) cari PATH >> edit >> cari apakah ada path nodejs Kamu?
3. Restart IDE (Visual Studi Code)
4. Try again😊

5. Open Terminal di VS Code
6. (Ketik) node coba.js

7. Selimit Mentry hehehe🤗
